Package: surveymapR
Type: Package
Title: Create Maps Around Survey Transects or Points
Version: 0.5.1
Author: Georg Andersson
Maintainer: Georg Andersson <georg.andersson@biol.lu.se>
Description: This package creates maps that show an overview and site-specific detail of
    transects and points in a biodiversity survey. Maps are rendered as PDFs suitable
    for field use. Supports multiple datasource types from the Swedish Butterfly
    Monitoring Scheme (SeBMS) and related monitoring programmes.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    sf,
    magick,
    htmlwidgets,
    purrr,
    tibble,
    tidyr,
    leaflet,
    leaflet.providers,
    readr,
    glue,
    quarto,
    mapview,
    pdftools
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
